= <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span> Congress

The <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span> has suffered severe internal conflicts the past year over Hugenberg's leadership, the Young Plan referendum with its controversial "imprisonment" paragraph[? if young_plan_signatures >= 10:, the impending vote on it within the Reichstag ?], and the expulsion of their Reichstag member Gottfried Treviranus over a private letter suggesting a split within the party if Hugenberg is unable to be removed.

The "unity of the no" against Marxism has been losing its force over the years, and the referendum against the Young Plan has only exacerbated internal party tensions. However, Hugenberg's efforts to increase control over the party will make it more difficult to force him out. [? if young_plan_signatures < 10: The failure of the initiative against the Young Plan has strengthened the dissidents position. ?] [? if tariffs > 0: The increase in tariffs has emboldened the agrarian wing go against Hugenberg's <i>Katastrophenpolitik</i>. ?]

